org.openscience.cdk.qsar.model.R
Class LinearRegressionModelFit

java.lang.Object
  org.openscience.cdk.qsar.model.R.LinearRegressionModelFit
Deprecated. 

public class LinearRegressionModelFit
extends java.lang.Object

A class that wraps the return value from R function, lm.. This is an internal class used by R to return the result of the call to lm. As a result it should not be instantiated by the user. The actual modeling class, LinearRegressionModel, provides acess to the various fields of this object.

Author:
Rajarshi Guha
Requires:
r-project
Belongs to CDK module:
qsar
